  "texts": [
    "Hence, practitioners can focus on these areas, tailoring their approach to specific project demands.",
    "In conclusion, our study offers a valuable instrument for practitioners aiming to amplify the success likelihood of their 6G-SQC projects.",
    "We now summarize the implications of this study in Sect. 7.1.",
    "The potential threats to the validity of study findings are presented in Sect. 7.2.",
    "The implications of this research are multi-fold and can significantly contribute to the practical, theoretical, and policy aspects of 6G-SQC projects:"
  ]
